<p class="eyebrow">Company</p>
<h1>Wholesale communications for teams that need engineering depth.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel builds and operates communications services for developers, telecom engineers, service providers, and businesses that need transparent pricing, practical migration paths, and support from people who understand the network.</p>
<p class="hero-actions">
	<a class="btn btn-primary" href="/signup/">Free trial</a>
	<a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact/">Contact us</a>
</p>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel has built networks for national carriers on a consultation basis — that engineering experience is embedded in every product we ship and every customer we support.</p>

<section class="section-block" data-section-type="positioning">
	<h2>What VoiceTel does</h2>
	<div class="oss-cards">
		<article class="oss-card">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "code-slash" %}</span>
				<h3 class="oss-card__title">Programmable Voice</h3>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description"><a href="/voiceml/">VoiceML</a>-compatible call control, signed webhooks, recordings, conferences, queues, streams, and <a href="/voiceml/migrate/">migration guidance</a>.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="oss-card">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "diagram-3" %}</span>
				<h3 class="oss-card__title">Wholesale network services</h3>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description"><a href="/voice/">Voice</a> origination and termination, <a href="/sip-trunking/">SIP trunking</a>, <a href="/numbers/">numbers</a>, porting, emergency-service configuration, and caller identity services (<a href="/caller-lookup/">Caller Lookup</a>, <a href="/carrier-lookup/">Carrier Lookup</a>).</p>
		</article>
		<article class="oss-card">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "chat-text" %}</span>
				<h3 class="oss-card__title">Application messaging</h3>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description"><a href="/messaging/">SMS and MMS</a> transport with A2P 10DLC support, delivery visibility, and high-volume planning.</p>
		</article>
		<article class="oss-card">
			<header class="oss-card__header">
				<span class="oss-card__icon">{% icon "telephone-fill" %}</span>
				<h3 class="oss-card__title">Business calling</h3>
			</header>
			<p class="oss-card__description"><a href="/pbx/">Hosted PBX</a>, <a href="/phone/applications/">VoiceTel Phone</a>, and <a href="/sdn/">SDN appliance</a> options for organizations that want VoiceTel to operate more of the stack.</p>
		</article>
